    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2006 Mitsubishi Lancer Evolution IX MR, a definitive pinnacle of the CT9A platform. This specimen features the legendary 2.0L 4G63 inline-four, equipped with MIVEC variable valve timing and a twin-scroll TD05HR-16G6C-10.5T turbocharger, delivering exceptional volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission, feeding power through an Active Center Differential (ACD) with three selectable modes for tarmac, gravel, and snow. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, complemented by Bilstein monotube dampers and forged BBS aluminum wheels which significantly reduce unsprung weight. Braking performance is maintained by Brembo four-piston front calipers acting on ventilated rotors. This vehicle displays zero signs of thermal cycling fatigue on the manifold or oxidation on the undercarriage, preserving its original factory tolerances and structural integrity. A truly unmolested, collector-quality example for the serious driving enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
